snippet.title: Snack Attack II
snippet.description:
On the surface, Funtastic's 1982 PC game Snack Attack II looks like just another Pac-Man clone. The game adds quite a few new twists to the Pac-Man formula however, such as selectable skill levels, secret doors, varying enemy speeds and speed boosting bonuses. All of this results in a great game that stands alone.

http://www.mobygames.com/game/pc-booter/snack-attack-ii
